13→/**
14→ * SidebarRow — V2: Jony Ive
15→ *
16→ * Active: bg-selection (warm white in light, elevated in dark)
17→ * Hover: 4% foreground overlay (barely visible, theme-agnostic)
18→ * Padding: repo=8px 12px, workspace/action=10px 12px
19→ * Workspace items use same left padding as repo — alignment comes from 20x20 icon wrappers.
20→ */
